16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
18 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
19 There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma School of Science
20 and Mathematics from any monies not otherwise appropriated from the
21 General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal year
22 ending June 30, 2027, the sum of Ninety-three Thousand Dollars
23 ($93,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to perform the
24
